---
title: HelloHero: Caribbean Chicken & Slaw Tacos with Pineapple & Peanuts
description: A dinner time fave is being whipped up tonight. Chicken tacos that are glazed and topped with juicy and sweet pineapple. Go crazy and add a sprinkling of peanuts to enjoy these amazing tacos.

